parameters: The sign is broken and unreadable.
You can't read it from this direction.
It seems that you can't enter without any equipment.
I don't have any business here right now.

parameters.name: 007. ノリノリなシンキングタイム (saruyama)

parameters: Oh~ Hikaru. You came at just the right time.

What's up? You're not planning something weird again, are
you?
No, I just wanted to say that.
I wonder if I'll die unintentionally!

After the incident of the panty thief, the trust in Saruyama
has completely diminished, not to mention the recent
class trial...

It's written in the textbook as if it were a mathematical
formula.

Why is the title making it seem like I stole it when I
didn't steal anything?!
What's this, are you even doing mind reading now?
...In any case, it's about this cave.
Isn't it in just the right spot?
What do you mean by just right? Explain.
Hey, I mean, doesn't it smell like an adventure?
Well... I feel like our mental ages are somewhat similar.
Hikaru and I are in the same university!
You're not being cute at all!
The perfect joke I shared with Tsugumi...!
I want to see it, Mama...
You won't accept it, huh. So, you want to enter here?
Anyway, I have a feeling that there's something amazing!
Your intuition has never been right, has it?

And then, I think I went in earlier and couldn't see
anything, so I just came out as it is.
So, is there anything? Like a flashlight or something.
Saruyama became fascinated with being an adventurer!
Saruyama, with a strange pose, gazes at me with sparkling eyes.

If this were a game, it would be natural for there to be
amazing treasures inside the cave.
But I want to go, so I want you to come with me!
If we find it later, let's definitely go together!
